      Building scalable systems that handle <span class="text-primary font-semibold">100K+ users</span>.
      6+ years crafting enterprise-grade software, leading cross-functional teams,
      and bridging legacy infrastructure with modern cloud-native solutions.
    </p>

    <!-- Location -->
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
      <svg class="inline w-4 h-4 mr-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
